data.description: Seller's will consider a carpeting allowance. Coming soon 11/12/23 This is a 4 bedroom 3 bath brick ranch with finished walkout basement.  They had a plumbing leak and has since fixed it but did not repair the ceilings in the family room downstairs. Very open floor plan with vaulted ceilings. New gutters were installed in 2017, New roof in 2017, hot water heater, furnace, and A/C were installed according to the previous sellers around 2015. Wood burning fireplace in living room.  Main floor laundry.  Home has so much potential.  Open House will be 11/12/2023 Sellers are cleaning carpets.
